Continue on Tic-Tac-Toe game

1) Draw the current state of the board
2) Get next position (1 - 9) as input from user IF there are remaining positions left
3) Check if given position is valid (is empty);
4) If given position is valid; put the symbol (X or O; according to turn)
5) Check for winning state; (horizontal, vertical and diagonals)
6) If there is winning condition; declare the current player as Winner.
7) Else go to (1)

